**/nvim/.netrwhist
**/nvim/plugged/**
**/nvim/sessions/**
**/karabiner/automatic_backups/**
packer_compiled.vim
packer_compiled.lua
.zshenv.secrets
.DS_Store
*.log
**/herdr/session.json
